**First.Name.More.Four:** List all the first names of authors in alphabetical order and
the count of times more than four the name appears.  
If the name appears less than four time, display null.  
% answer = '''
WITH C1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(*) as C
              FROM Authors
              Group by first_name
              HAVING c>4),
C2 AS (SELECT DISTINCT first_name, count(*) as C
              FROM Authors
              Group by first_name)

SELECT C2.first_name, C1.c-4
  FROM C2
  LEFT JOIN C1
  ON C1.C = C2.C
  ORDER BY C2.first_name
'''
{{!sql(answer, dbs=dbs, row=10, points=25, name='First.Name.More.Four')}}
% include('viewAnswer')

